title: and the Baby Mamas - Brittany Cartwright & Stassi Schroeder
description:
It’s the girls turn, and first things first, Brittany Cartwright responds to Stassi and Lala’s daughters not being able to date her & Jax Taylor’s son!  The gals get real about pregnancy symptoms and morning sickness, conception stories, and the reality of a #PumpRules pregnancy pact. They speak to their biggest fears about childbirth, motherhood, and what they’re especially loving about their baby daddies during this time! They also put internet trolls on notice, and share plans for the future!
